- report-form.tsx's serial-number dropdown called /api/vehicles/list to
  preload the full vehicle list for client-side filtering as you type,
  but that route never existed (only /api/vehicles/[serial] and
  /api/vehicles/search did) - every request 404'd, allVehicles stayed
  empty, and the dropdown never appeared no matter what was typed. The
  underlying listVehicles() data-layer function already existed in
  src/lib/db.ts; it just had no route wired up to it. Added the route.
- added an explicit ค้นหา (search) button next to the serial input that
  calls the existing /api/vehicles/search endpoint (Supabase + live
  Tractor IN sheet) and merges results into the dropdown - covers units
  not yet in the preloaded list and lets users trigger a search
  manually instead of relying only on the as-you-type filter. Enter key
  in the field triggers the same manual search.
